Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How she adjusting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing fine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's made a lot of new friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrific
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's fitting in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah that's really good news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's becoming used to her new school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting to be quite late
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now before I forget
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some pictures their new ones of Rosemary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to see her in person
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 2 days from now we could meet here again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fact is I'm completely sober my life's back to normal again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually this may be the first time my life's been truly normal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally clear to me how much I've screwed up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to let her decide whether she wants to see you or not
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really hoping she will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard I have to go now or I'll be late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just more coffee please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr rifine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your impression of this man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something Richard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely why do you think you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here for counseling I asked a questions remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I've told you before I'm a doctor not a fortune teller
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right you're inside comes from your years of experience with patience
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's the boy in the photo this time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A person of interest in my case
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He made the initial discovery of Edmond Farms body at the alleged suicide scene
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly he's a friend of the deceased that's all I know well here's what I know Richard yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a dedicated workahol
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got to learn to take time for yourself to relax I'm beginning to do just that we'll wonders never
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese and doctor I have news
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About what
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosemary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to see her very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you must be looking forward to that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah but just remember
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do get to see her you can't get back the time you've lost you need to be emotionally prepared for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Changes in her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what and listen you must not touch a drop of alcohol am I clear don't worry I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't I suppose you're off to work on your case again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave yet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time to talk about the event that got you kicked off the police force tell me Richard what do you remember from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I remember all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He was 16 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And a suspected murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been drinking on the job when I spotted him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My shot I'm dead
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He died because I was drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You faced up to it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't erase it it will always be there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing can remove that memory from your head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you know what's important now giving myself permission to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You may step to the Head of the Class do I get an A+ Professor not so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give out perfect scores easily I demand results and besides I'm not all that crazy about perfect patience
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're boring frankly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Neumann
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A business admin student in the economics department at Munich University apparently he told that prostitute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposing is Margo Langer that he too is shoe volts real son
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I don't know whether he was telling the truth or not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However I need to investigate that possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes excuse me I finished all the cleaning so I'll be going now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning for you is never hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare for a man living by himself to be so neat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes my job here extremely Pleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well lately I've been trying to clean up my act on all fronts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but notice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a new picture of your daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to see her soon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really that's just wonderful your daughter will be so delighted do you really think so of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What young girl wouldn't be happy to see her father
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah it was a tough one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So were you able to turn your paper in on time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Norman I can't figure you out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know for sure then why haven't you told shuvall that you're his son
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just another con man or are you the real deal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're legit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is stopping you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize that any parent would be overjoyed just to see their own child
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she doesn't want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's made up her mind I didn't want to force her it's her decision hey that's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I get for you sir
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just go where he is and you can find us there no you can't oh Carl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're all grown up you can meet your father if you want don't hate him if he turns you away promise me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That no matter what because Mommy doesn't hate him keep
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This with you always it was a gift from your father on the day you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With none to admire them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The daffodils of Loris proudly bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With none to mind them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trees of Peoria Russell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The bloody tracks of the nameless man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say Norman you come a long way and become an excellent reader
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed by how much your Latin has improved in the short time you've been reading for me to be perfectly honest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being tutored by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well he certainly is an excellent teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he be anybody I know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert is my tutor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A proficient young man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And not only in Latin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an extensive knowledge of Law and economics and amazing aptitude in fact for whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Studies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a boy who's beautifully gifted at everything he's True Perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr shoe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you think if a boy like him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Yohan Liebert was actually your real son
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I'd ever seen him smile
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it clear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're worthy enough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To be his son Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest I was jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter which way I looked at it you came off better than me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to admit it but I do envy you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Carl what have you got to lose go ahead and tell you his real son will you stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times must I tell you I have no intention of doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be the point if I did
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And worse than that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he'll think of me as just another greedy Predator only interested in getting hold of his fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll despise me forever
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How my mother lived her life until her death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And with everything I've gone through up till now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows nothing about me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't stand for him thinking I'm after his fortune when he doesn't know a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why you should go talk to him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to gain his trust make him understand the truth about his son
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never believe that I miss son
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well don't you have something from your past that would prove it to him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything he might recognize or remember
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something you both could recall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Far as I know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Think back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drawing a big blank it doesn't matter I don't want to tell him okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case can you explain why you spend all that time having me tutor you in Latin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it because you wanted to please him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you wanted to make him proud of you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking that maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should quit my job being his reader
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the best
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your concern I appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I'm done
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you're entitled to know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have something that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can prove who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what is it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dumb I don't know why I'm still holding on to it I'm not going to convince him and I don't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My foster parents are coming to visit me next week
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fooling myself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the son he'd want to have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When your mind's made up it's important not to waver so for the time being Carl I think it would be a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Idea to let me keep an eye on your proof
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so happy to hear your studies are going well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right mother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been worried about you Kyle I want to make sure you're eating right I'm always eating out so I know I have to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Have to be careful not to gain any weight better stay away from your mother's cooking too but it's so delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your social life son
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making a lot of new friends here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some people I hang out with and can talk to you about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrific
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always good to have friends yes that's very true and it looks to us like you're doing quite well
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm extremely grateful to both of you
